summary: Built as a production ready reference to the Object RTC specification (originally designed in the W3C WebRtc Community Group), WebRtc Lib is a secure, fast and highly performant developer toolkit enabling real-time voice calling, video chat and data functionality (file transfer etc.) for mobile, desktop and web. If you are integrating real-time voice, video or data into your mobile or web app and want WebRtc and WebRTC compatibility, WebRtc Lib is the solution for you.
